    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-04-10T16:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-04-10T16:00:00-05:00" n="359"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d359">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.77/359</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Harbin</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_MCK1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Moser</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-04-10T17:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 10, 1918, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>For <persName corresp="#p_SJF1">Stevens</persName> from <persName
                        corresp="#p_FSM1">Felton</persName>:<note n="1" xml:id="d359fn1">See
                        footnote 2, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_222">p.
                        222</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p>Your April 10, 11 a.m., just received. Russian Embassy and Department gratified.
                    Your work regarded as of prime importance and once abandoned very difficult to
                    resume. Keep us advised your progress.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
